	measure 'SNP Care Management: Number of reassessments completed (Element F)' = SNP Care Management: Number of reassessments completed (Element F)

	measure 'SNP Care Management: Number of reassessments refused (Element G)' = SNP Care Management: Number of reassessments refused (Element G)

	measure 'SNP Care Management: Number of reassessments where enrollee was unable to be reached (Element H)' = SNP Care Management: Number of reassessments where enrollee was unable to be reached (Element H)

	measure 'Total number of enrollment requests' = Total number of enrollment requests

	measure 'Total number of enrollment requests requiring additional information' = Total number of enrollment requests requiring additional information

	measure 'Total number of voluntary disenrollment transactions' = Total number of voluntary disenrollment transactions

	measure 'Rewards and Incentives Programs: Number of currently enrolled members (Element G)' = Rewards and Incentives Programs: Number of currently enrolled members (Element G)

	measure 'Rewards and Incentives Programs: Number of rewards made so far (Element H)' = Rewards and Incentives Programs: Number of rewards made so far (Element H)

	measure 'Payments to Providers: Total actual payments made to contracted providers (Element A)' = Payments to Providers: Total actual payments made to contracted providers (Element A)

